{
  "chapter": 251,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙在临淄街头寻找失踪的手下雷允儿等人，得知他们因欠债被仲孙龙的人抓走。途中偶遇齐国司库大夫解子元，一个惧内却坦诚友善的官员，解子元主动驾车送他前往仲孙府。抵达后项少龙发现仲孙龙正在接见楚国权臣李园，而李园一眼认出他。项少龙以凤菲管事身份与仲孙龙谈判，面对威胁毫不畏惧，先以身法制服两名武士，又掷匕首震慑全场。在李园的斡旋下，仲孙龙被迫释放雷允儿等人。李园主动送项少龙离开，既保护他的安全，也让仲孙龙不敢事后报复。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其他人呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_chun",
      "speaker_name": "费淳",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "逛窰子去了！我们正要找地方喝酒，沈管事一起来吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_fei_chun",
      "text": "知否他们到哪间窰子去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "另一人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "昂贵的当然没他们份儿，沈管事只要看哪一间门面最简陋，保证可找到他们。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_fei_chun",
      "text": "事情有变，张副管事告诉我大小姐开罪了这处一个有势力的人，怕他虽不敢碰大小姐，却拿我们这些下人开刀，所以你们略微遣兴之后，得立即回去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "发生什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "路人甲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "欠了仲孙爷钱财还胆敢来逛窰子，怕是不知道'死'字是怎样写的。唉！像一群狗儿般被人拖走，真是羞人。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那些人是我的朋友，现在只好拿钱为他们赎身，请问仲孙爷的府第在哪里？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "路人乙",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "千万不要告诉我夫人……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兄台误会，我只是要问路。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "路人乙",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "差点给你吓死，问路也不用拉着人的衣衫嘛！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只是心切找仲孙龙大爷的府第，小弟是他的远房亲戚，特来向他问好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "路人乙",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "仲孙府在南大街，刚好是我家的斜对面，让我送你一程吧！唉！我也要快点回家。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "路人乙",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我特意要马车停在这里，好使没人知道我逛青楼去。嘿！还未请教兄台高姓大名。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我叫沈良，兄台呢？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "路人乙",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我叫解子元，来！上车吧！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "媛媛的皮肤娇嫩得像锦缎，又顺得人意，只恨不能留在那里度宿。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "贵夫人长得很丑吗？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "当然不是！媛媛虽有点姿色，但比起她来仍差远了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那解兄为何还要到外边拈花惹草？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不要以为我对她日久生厌，事实上我对她是愈看愈爱，也愈是怕她。而若有起口角争执，娘总是帮她不帮我，皆因她替娘生下两个白白胖胖的孙儿。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "解兄之所以要到外边偷偷胡混，怕是要尝尝贵夫人所欠奉的柔顺滋味吧！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "还是沈兄明白我，哈！沈兄可否帮我一个大忙？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我可以怎样助你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你能否扮作是我不见多时的朋友，远道前来探我？那我自然要竭诚招待，如此我就可溜出来久一点了。嘿！我自然不会薄待你，沈兄的花费全包在小弟身上。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这两天我很忙，怕不能到贵府拜访。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "只要花一点时间就成，明晚好吗？申时后我在舍下等待沈兄的大驾。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我尽量抽时间来吧！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "沈兄真够朋友。唉！说出来恐怕你不肯相信，我解子元怎么说都是位居司库大夫的官儿，可是却无人敢陪我到青楼去，纵然有美相伴，但独酌无友，总令人扫兴，现在有沈兄相陪就好哩！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你的朋友是否给尊夫人骂怕了？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "是打怕了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "解权",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "大少爷！快到仲孙爷的府第了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "解权现在是唯一仍忠心于我的人。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "先送沈爷进去，然后我们才回家。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "恕小弟虽把沈兄送到这里，却不能久候，因我必须于亥时前回去，惹怒了她，小弟就有祸哩！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "解兄似和仲孙大爷非常稔熟？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "算是有点关系吧！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "人与人间是要讲点机缘的，不知如何我一见沈兄便心中欢喜，更晓得沈兄是交得过的朋友。嘿！明晚记得来啊！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "鲍光",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "小人鲍光，请解大人下车。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "本官只是送仲……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不是他的亲戚。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_bao_guang",
      "text": "是送本官的一位好友沈良来拜见仲孙大爷，仲孙大爷在家吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "鲍光",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "原来是沈爷，大爷正在接见楚国来的贵客。小人这就进去通传，不知沈爷想小人如何向大爷报上？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不耽阻解兄，明晚我定会来的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "鲍光",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "沈爷请进去先避风雪再说吧！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_bao_guang",
      "text": "鲍兄请通知仲孙大爷，说我是为凤菲的事来见他的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "鲍光",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "大爷请沈兄进去。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "鲍光",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "大爷知道沈爷是解大人朋友，方肯接见沈爷。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "鲍仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈爷到！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "仲孙龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "坐！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "仲孙龙",
      "listener": "char_li_yuan",
      "text": "李相国可知我为何既肯立即接见这籍籍无名的人，又肯让他对坐？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "李园",
      "listener": "char_zhong_sun_long",
      "text": "龙爷行事总是出人意表，我怎猜估得到。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "仲孙龙",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "皆因此人是由解子元送来，所以我必须有所交代。使得将来解子元问起来，亦不会怪我没有看他的情面。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "仲孙龙",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "报上身份来意，与解子元是何关系？若我觉得你有半句谎言，保证你永远不能凭自己两条腿离开这里。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "仲孙龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有什么好笑？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhong_sun_long",
      "text": "我笑的是原来名动天下的仲孙龙，只是个恃强凌弱的人，难怪凤菲小姐看不入眼。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "李园",
      "listener": "char_zhong_sun_long",
      "text": "住手！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "仲孙龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "退回去！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "仲孙龙",
      "listener": "char_li_yuan",
      "text": "李相国为何阻止我教训这个狂妄的家伙？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "李园",
      "listener": "char_zhong_sun_long",
      "text": "若我是龙爷，会教这些擅作主张的奴才全体捱棍子，怎可在龙爷尚未有说话之前便邀功动手，那说不定会害了龙爷一命。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "仲孙龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "害我一命？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还是李相国高明，看！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhong_sun_long",
      "text": "现在我们可以好好一谈吧！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_sun_long",
      "speaker_name": "仲孙龙",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "好！就凭你这手玩艺，说吧！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_li_yuan",
      "text": "李相国高明，竟看出我沈良尚有后招。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "李园",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "只看沈兄神态冷若冰雪，便知你是个第一流的刺客。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhong_sun_long",
      "text": "我沈良乃凤菲小姐手下的管事，助她打理团内的大小事务，至于与解子元则是肝胆相照的好友，但若龙爷要动手分出生死，却不须把这点关系放在心上。我沈良既敢来此，已抱着宁为玉碎，不作瓦全的心。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "李园",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "「宁为玉碎，不作瓦全」！这句话很有意思。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_sun_long",
      "speaker_name": "仲孙龙",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你确有说话的资格，不过若妄想与我仲孙龙对抗，实属不智。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "李园",
      "listener": "char_zhong_sun_long",
      "text": "龙爷可否听李园这中间人，说句公道话。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_sun_long",
      "speaker_name": "仲孙龙",
      "listener": "char_li_yuan",
      "text": "李相国请说。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "李园",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我想先请沈兄保证不再发暗器，大家才坦诚对话。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_li_yuan",
      "text": "相国吩咐，我沈良怎敢不从，何况我一向仰慕龙爷，今趟只是逼不得已，万望龙爷大人有大量，原谅则个。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_sun_long",
      "speaker_name": "仲孙龙",
      "listener": "char_li_yuan",
      "text": "李相国对此有何高见？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "李园",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "沈兄此来，未知所因何事？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhong_sun_long",
      "text": "只是来向龙爷求个人情，望他高抬贵手，放回在下几名伙伴，免致凤菲小姐为难。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "李园",
      "listener": "char_zhong_sun_long",
      "text": "这中间怕是有误会吧！龙爷怎会和那些奴才计较？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_sun_long",
      "speaker_name": "仲孙龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁把凤小姐的手下拿起来？究竟是否真有此事？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "仲孙龙手下",
      "listener": "char_zhong_sun_long",
      "text": "刚才确有人在青楼闹事，还和我们的人发生冲突，故把他们拿了回来，准备明早送官，却不知原来是沈管事的人。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_sun_long",
      "speaker_name": "仲孙龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还不立即尽数释放，给我送回凤小姐处。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "李园",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "沈管事身手不凡，胆识过人，我李园非常欣赏，不若由我送沈兄一程，顺便聊聊。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 251,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 418
    }
  ],
